{"tid":1506273,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實民間記招真係要黑警同政府記招學下野","createTime":"2019-08-25T18:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T00:01:40.000Z","uid":245409,"like":113,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c319783f1d10ccc259c476046ba4113a999e0bec","tid":1506273,"uid":245409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"句句暴徒前暴徒後，又話極暴力同極度激進，極度核心暴力份子<br />\n<br />\n句句都踩到你地底泥咁，將對方所有野講到無惡不作咁，再將自己人講成英雄咁，超厚面皮<br />\n<br />\n佢地曝光率係極高，日日用呢d詞彙洗人腦，而且無線會cut落黎係黃金時段重播再重播<br />\n<br />\n最好每一句都黑警前黑警後，極度核心暴力黑警，打住警察旗號既恐怖份子，視人命如草芥，完全失控的激進行為&hellip;之類<br />\n<br />\n呢d詞彙要多到無線想cut到cut唔到，就算節錄一兩句都要聽到黑警，暴力警魔呢d詞，要入屋！<br />\n<br />\n學下野啦！人善被人欺"},{"pid":"96e90b11c1f82509c96a299549c2e3f1f5cc4a9a","tid":1506273,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"香港人！還拖！往死裏打！<br />\n826稅局，828#Metoo，831民陣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">901開始無限期癱瘓機場<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貨運</span></span></span></strong>，902三罷<br />\n全面批鬥警犬及其家屬！<br />\n㩒錢/換美金，經濟制裁中共！"},{"pid":"acd36b7875002ea1f69f01d1854387095c2d9b1a","tid":1506273,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"借po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小心個袋俾狗咬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506145/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506145/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5955e6f08576c719993c520951c9697f0fdea106","tid":1506273,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee48843077a14c4eea5b887aae52dc7e8572863","tid":1506273,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:06:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 :